resources.description: Each industry has been impacted with the emergence of the Internet and e-commerce in the global market.of course, the equipment manufacturing is no exception facing the global market, resource, technology and talent competition. The author introduced the current situation of equipment manufacturing and analyzed the facing problems and obstacles in developing e-commerce in equipment manufacturing industry. Some corresponding measures and suggestions were put forward.
resources.name: Discussion on the Problems and Countermeasures in the Development of E-Commerce in Equipment Manufacturing Industry
